# Working notes, drafts, and planning documents I keep local-only.
# Everything under _private/ is for my eyes only and never gets committed.
_private/

# Per-post draft text - the post.md inside each posts/<date-slug>/ folder.
# Materials in the same folder (templates, snippets) ARE committed; the post
# text itself lives on the blog platform, not in the repo.
posts/**/post.md

